 I
think that Democratic staffers often are so stuck in their ways of how the =
media used to be, that they=E2=80=99re not able to think about how indie me=
dia operates and also think about the opportunities that it presents.</p><p=
 style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margi=
n-bottom:0px;"><strong>The Harris campaign made a big deal out of their Tik=
